勁既10號阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上半場一開波阿根廷同法國快打快係on99<br />\n咩叫失果幾球可以避免到 反cup 2-1 比人世界波追到再反輸 唔攻等輸阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？係阿 避免到 咪輸到尾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好扮識波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>西班牙中場係老姐,邊有慢?<br />\n佢地對中堅都冇阿根廷呢隊咁離譜啦<br />\n事實唔主攻既話包皮個2球都未必會失<br />\n不過你話體力問題就真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母恩尼斯達大衛施華isco哥斯達巴斯基斯高基thiago 邊一個係快架 唔好講快啦 邊個唔慢？<br />\n唔識唔好衝出黎柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1183ea68933bd301083cb932892408f1eb070ab","tid":723890,"uid":87394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a033035c2ad22088315a561470fe12bb5754e92","tid":723890,"uid":77771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b1c280a1197dc303dee4975b8124555ae8b172","tid":723890,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc40afba7b9a28102a531ab144097e453d6d5e55","tid":723890,"uid":77771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"美斯都跑唔起，仲要佢自己喺前面搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"你邊下見到美斯跑唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:07:28.000Z","msg":"今屆又係散步帝，你叫佢喺前面自己衝<br />\n<br />\n你用屎忽睇波？<br />\n<br />\n自己睇吓佢平均跑動有幾多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"依家要佢係中場造波跑乜春<br />\n冇野做突然係場邊跑比你睇呀?"}]}